snippet.title: Jury finds Kyle Rittenhouse not guilty on all charges
snippet.description:
ABC News’ Phil Lipof speaks with legal expert Channa Lloyd about the Kyle Rittenhouse not guilty verdict, and what it says about self-defense and vigilantism laws in America.

ABC News Live Prime, Weekdays at 7EST & 9EST
